---
title: Voice conversation — single turn
---
%% Last updated: 2026-05-29
%% Scope: One full conversational turn — user speaks, coach replies — annotated with realistic
%%        latencies for an EU user (Lausanne) against the production stack.
%% Total wall-clock from "user stops speaking" to "first coach audio plays": ~1.8 s.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant App as Mobile app
    participant Fly as Fly API (Stockholm)
    participant DB as Supabase Postgres
    participant DG as Deepgram (us-east)
    participant AI as OpenAI (us-east)
    participant TTS as OpenAI TTS (us-east)
    participant Store as Supabase Storage

    User->>App: Tap mic, speak
    App->>App: expo-audio captures PCM 16 kHz mono

    App->>Fly: Open WebSocket /voice/turn<br/>Authorization: Bearer access_token
    Fly->>Fly: Verify JWT (cached JWKS)
    Fly->>DG: Open Deepgram streaming socket

    loop While user speaks
        App->>Fly: Audio chunk (binary frame)
        Fly->>DG: Forward chunk
        DG-->>Fly: Partial transcript (every ~300 ms)
    end

    User->>App: Stops speaking
    DG-->>Fly: Final transcript (~400 ms after silence)

    Fly->>DB: SELECT conversation history WHERE user_id = ...
    DB-->>Fly: messages[] (~5 ms — same DC)

    Note over Fly,AI: Build chat request: system prompt + history + new user message.

    Fly->>AI: POST /chat/completions (SSE, streaming)<br/>~100 ms RTT
    AI-->>Fly: First token (~500-800 ms)

    rect rgb(253, 231, 209)
        Note over Fly: Sentence buffer:<br/>accumulate tokens until punctuation,<br/>then ship sentence to TTS in parallel<br/>with continuing to stream more tokens.
    end

    par Stream more tokens
        loop Until LLM done
            AI-->>Fly: Token chunk
        end
    and Synthesize earlier sentences
        Fly->>TTS: POST /audio/speech (sentence N)
        TTS-->>Fly: MP3 bytes (~400 ms first chunk)
    end

    Fly->>Store: Upload audio chunk for cache
    Fly-->>App: WebSocket binary frame: audio chunk
    App->>App: expo-audio decodes + plays
    App->>User: Coach voice (first sound ~1.8 s after silence)

    Note over Fly,DB: After turn ends:<br/>Fly persists user + coach messages,<br/>bumps conversations.updated_at,<br/>records usage_events for billing.
